summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 232 W, Page 26 of the Official Land Use Map of the City of Seattle adopted by Ordinance 110570 to rezone certain property located in Block 4, plat of North Park, from Residental, Multi-family, Low-rise 2 (L-2 and Multiple Residence Low Density RM 800 Zones to Community Business (BC) Zone (Petition of Evelyn B. Richter; C.F. 291534).
